Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:05.58,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.22,0:00:07.82,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:16.70,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you get to know that from Keigo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.69,0:00:19.83,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Since after the summer festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.29,0:00:22.40,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.40,0:00:25.62,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Last time, when I was still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.98,0:00:29.05,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,He rejected a really nice opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.48,0:00:32.46,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.53,0:00:33.47,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.47,0:00:36.38,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we were friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:37.23,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiraishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.23,0:00:40.72,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that I was the only one who thought we were friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:41.45,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.45,0:00:42.35,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.76,0:00:44.13,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.31,0:00:46.02,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka-cha-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.50,0:00:49.65,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.07,0:00:55.49,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't consider you as my friend any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.89,0:01:01.67,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,With this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.90,0:01:05.04,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Underwear Society is history!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:53.33,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:03:01.03,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have two bad news today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:06.87,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to her brother's work, our class representative Hayama Nayu, is transferring to another school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:11.79,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because this is happening so suddenly, she won't be able to attend classes anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:15.66,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we write her a card or something once we've calmed down?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:21.55,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,The other bad news is about the fire last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:26.10,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, Mizuno-sensei's apartment was completely burned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:29.64,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be careful with fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:34.41,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Things have really become interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.41,0:03:36.19,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's almost winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:37.20,RM main 2,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:38.71,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:40.57,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer up, Mizuno-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:42.70,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can come talk to me any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:45.95,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:52.71,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Hayama will be transferring now, we'll have to select a new class representative, so let's start voting...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.57,0:03:55.93,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we doing about the society today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:03:59.09,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:09.54,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:11.04,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:12.39,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.61,0:04:16.90,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can we visit the Underwear Society some time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:18.42,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:21.18,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. Hayama-san is leaving, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:22.90,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll keep running it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:25.12,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:32.21,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,But... now that Nayu-chan is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:35.04,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your bra is cute, Shiraishi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:36.80,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you make it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.80,0:04:39.46,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just made some changes to something I bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:42.34,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of an Underwear Society member.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.18,0:04:46.05,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be wearing bras one size larger now, Terumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:47.25,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:50.09,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a regular at the fittings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:53.27,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll go attend one as well next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:04:59.12,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting late!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:07.57,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's everyone getting so emotional?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:09.53,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after showing them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:12.30,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the Society will be off today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:15.64,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,There won't be any point in having it when Mizuno-sensei is in that state.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:20.98,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Hayama-san isn't here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:25.46,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,The society didn't even last a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:30.36,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've got a photo shoot to attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.41,0:05:38.74,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like she's busy working for magazines these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:42.87,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home as well. I've got to get ready for an upcoming match.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.29,0:05:56.58,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? Compared to someone whose home burned down, transferring isn't anything big!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:05:59.50,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally quiet enough to study in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:09.42,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we really not do anything without Hayama around?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:11.60,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:17.34,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... so the Underwear Society has become inactive, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:21.55,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,When things were finally starting to get interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:32.00,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently Hayama-san's too busy moving to come to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:33.51,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:39.46,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to confess your feelings to that Senpai of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.19,0:06:46.69,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:49.77,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,But before that, have you thought about where you are going to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:54.18,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well you can stay at my place for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.11,0:07:02.58,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:09.03,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.17,0:07:15.19,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,That has nothing to do with underwear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:18.04,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess now's not the time for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.93,0:07:25.80,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,How long is Haruka planning to sit there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:27.09,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.63,0:07:37.93,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I say something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:46.65,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to say now, Nayu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:58.07,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do for these girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.91,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have seen this scene before somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.34,0:08:27.45,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Komachi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.45,0:08:31.19,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, you didn't know my name at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:34.76,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you waiting for Keigo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:36.23,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.23,0:08:37.27,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your umbrella?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.27,0:08:39.35,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was sunny this afternoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:47.79,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Shiraishi now just keeps staring at the field after school these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.53,0:08:52.46,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,She runs away when that forehead freak tries to talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:08:59.71,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've tried mailing her, but I haven't gotten a reply yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:06.98,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I had finally made some friends, but I'm all alone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:09.35,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.71,0:09:13.71,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Komachi-kun-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.73,0:09:17.24,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can borrow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.98,0:09:27.92,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it! I finally got you, Yako!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:33.42,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you started wearing a sports bra, I'm not the same as I used to be either!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.49,0:09:39.18,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you gotten a bit shorter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.70,0:09:52.65,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not acting like yourself. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.55,0:10:31.36,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,We all change slowly over time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.07,0:10:34.46,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just stay in the same place forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:45.02,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let things go like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:49.25,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let Haruka and Nayu part without making up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.66,0:10:55.83,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for all or nothing, else you are not a true warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.11,0:11:08.14,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to keep sitting there, Haruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.53,0:11:17.28,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks at this. These are the leftovers from Mizuno-sensei's swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:21.46,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,From the overnighter. Do you think she'd be happy to have them back?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:24.70,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she said she doesn't have anything left from that accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:26.95,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys should focus on moving your hands, not your mouths.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:29.25,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your help, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:31.31,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.38,0:11:34.03,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you find anything you can use, you can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:35.88,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:39.03,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to help as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:40.98,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:43.84,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we're done, let's go eat something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.75,0:11:47.97,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amahara's been doing nothing but complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:51.60,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,If she really didn't want to do it, she wouldn't have come prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:01.92,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:06.53,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,The textbooks I packed after so much effort!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.80,0:12:08.33,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Amahara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:09.46,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.46,0:12:11.70,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, please go help out with cleaning or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:13.97,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,What? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:22.47,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, why isn't Shiraishi-san here when {\i1}I am{\i0} helping out as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:28.84,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Haruka-chan must be busy with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:31.62,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Help her move?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.37,0:12:33.64,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave me alone already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.39,0:12:37.61,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Are you really OK with it, Haruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:41.07,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, why don't we take a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.12,0:12:45.27,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go prepare some tea, so you go buy some snacks for everyone, Nayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.27,0:12:46.34,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:51.75,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I had some good coffee around. I wonder if we already packed it away?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:53.58,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:12:58.58,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you have to say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:01.18,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you even invite Shiraishi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.18,0:13:02.65,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:05.75,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I came back empty handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:08.93,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they're still fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:13.14,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just force them to meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:35.87,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:38.37,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to call you so late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.87,0:13:39.84,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.86,0:13:46.05,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:48.76,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to come tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:51.47,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:56.99,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's leaving in two days. Tomorrow's your last chance to talk things out with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.88,0:13:59.08,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Last chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:03.48,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember the first time I wore a bra?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:08.67,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,You sprayed water all over me, and I wore the bra Nayu made.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:11.33,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sad as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:16.86,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,But if Nayu has decided to go with Keigo-san, I'd like her to go off with a smile on her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:19.61,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what friends do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.32,0:14:23.15,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,You should do it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:25.37,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yako-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:32.96,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Once Halloween is over, we'll be getting ready for winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:43.02,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,What will we be doing this time next year?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.41,0:14:46.78,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought her with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:05.51,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:11.46,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we get in the boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:25.57,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it alright to leave those two alone together?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:27.24,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.63,0:15:30.44,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,They both actually want to apologize to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:34.10,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are just too awkward, so they can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.77,0:15:37.92,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,They just have to take that step.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:40.29,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think either of them have the courage to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:46.58,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you think? I think they'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:51.97,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be fine. They both care about each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:56.74,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I didn't help you move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:15:59.89,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'm just glad I got to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.88,0:16:04.34,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was happy to get your texts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.34,0:16:08.54,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I did something so horrible to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:15.20,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept thinking all the time about how to reply you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:16.37,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:24.92,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew how you felt, but I was so sad you'd be leaving, I just couldn't help myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:27.45,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I made this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:29.43,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to eat it together?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.67,0:16:40.97,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:44.44,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:50.43,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought everyone would leave me if I told the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.29,0:16:54.96,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I did something terrible to all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:56.95,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:01.44,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Women's friendship is difficult, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:04.28,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:08.88,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:11.99,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you make up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.99,0:17:12.84,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.31,0:17:17.93,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we aren't together, we'll be able to run the Underwear Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:20.55,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,We have text messages, phones and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:23.56,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,During summer vacation, we can visit each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:28.29,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,She might be a troublemaker, but she's not so bad after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:31.03,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,You had me worried for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:32.46,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:35.80,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. It's just like you said, Haruka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:40.57,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have told you two right away about the transfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.57,0:17:41.74,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nayu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:46.00,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize not telling you would hurt you so much, Haruka-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.01,0:17:52.75,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hurt, too! Where are my eggs?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.41,0:17:53.20,RM main 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it easy, Yako-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:55.78,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going over there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:57.01,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yako-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.36,0:18:46.51,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:53.65,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't this how we became friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:55.28,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,You were sticking your butt way out, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.92,0:19:01.18,RM main 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely keep mailing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.18,0:19:03.14,RM main 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're far away, we'll always be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:05.81,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a bunch of idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:18.42,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go looking up people's skirts over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:23.05,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the dissatisfied expression?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:30.66,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nayu, looks like you've got a mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.01,0:19:38.36,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing! Amahara-san is a magazine model!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:48.83,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:51.98,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,She may have been suited to becoming a model.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:20:00.50,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll meet you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:07.38,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amahara-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.38,0:20:08.52,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:10.87,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nayu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:16.27,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I got these for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:20.84,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Komachi-kun, could you give one to Amahara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.17,0:20:22.28,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:25.07,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I'll treasure this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:33.42,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treasure the memories we've had these past six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.91,0:20:36.16,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:38.58,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the end, Nayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:41.56,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yako-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:45.67,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.39,0:20:47.35,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.91,0:21:01.55,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:06.87,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forget the time we've spent together here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.82,0:21:11.45,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.82,0:21:12.25,RM main 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Nayu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:12.25,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.65,0:22:43.17,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.13,0:22:49.63,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I go to the next Underwear Society meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.05,0:22:53.97,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. Take this as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.20,0:22:56.67,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.56,0:22:59.63,TL Note,,0000,0000,0000,,TL Note: The girl used a masculine first person pronoun earlier. Which is usually only used by men.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.56,0:22:59.63,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,What did she just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.31,0:23:01.31,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.09,0:23:04.79,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I could join your club?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.81,0:23:10.87,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Keigo-san said he would come back on weekends.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.54,0:23:16.03,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuno-sensei's going to stop by and check on me once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.40,0:23:19.59,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think we could work together again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.74,0:23:24.88,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.88,0:23:26.14,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nayu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.31,0:23:33.52,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.52,0:23:34.94,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you laughing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.94,0:23:36.75,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever leave us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.77,0:23:39.09,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka-chan, Yako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.15,0:23:31.30,RM main,,0000,0000,0000,,
